Old scenarios:
chasing small, selfish gains;
doing everything alone;
quitting when things get hard   New scenarios:
setting big, meaningful goals;
leading others toward higher income;
persisting until the finish line

Old scenarios: lying and misleading others; acting without a plan; being fake or dishonest.   New scenarios:
breaking old mental patterns;
using a clear strategy;
